\c 22
\s Utsvene hwezvipo
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 2 Taura kuna Aroni nekuvanakomana vake kuti vazvitsaure\x + Num. 6.3.\x* pazvinhu zvitsvene zvevana vaIsraeri\x + Rev. 22.3; Eki. 28.38; Det. 15.19.\x*, uye vasasvibisa zita rangu dzvene\x + Rev. 18.21.\x*, nokuti zvitsvene kwandiri. Ndini Jehovha.
\v 3 Uti kwavari: Ani nani kuvana venyu vose kumazera enyu, unopa kuzvinhu zvitsvene, vana vaIsraeri zvavanoita zvitsvene kuna Jehovha, kusachena kwake kuri paari\x + 7.20.\x*, mweya uyo uchagurwa kubva pachiso changu; ndini Jehovha\x + Eki. 30.33.\x*.
\v 4 Ani nani kuvana vaAroni ane maperembudzi kana kuyerera haangadyi pazvinhu zvitsvene kusvika achena\x + 14.2; 15.13.\x*, uye anogunzva chinhu chipi nechipi chakasvibiswa newakafa\x + Num. 19.11.\x*, kana munhu paari panobuda urume hwekusangana\x + 15.16.\x*.
\v 5 Kana ani nani anogunzva chipi nechipi chinokambaira chaangasvibiswa nacho\x + 11.24,43,44.\x*, kana munhu ave asina kuchena naye, maerereno nekusachena kwake kwose\x + 15.7,19.\x*.
\v 6 Mweya unogunzva izvo uchava usina kuchena kusvika madekwani, uye haungadyi pazvinhu zvitsvene, kunze kwekuti asuka nyama yake nemvura\x + 15.5-11; VaHeb. 10.22.\x*.
\v 7 Kana zuva ravira uchava wakachena; uye pashure uchadya pazvinhu zvitsvene; nokuti ndezvekudya zvake\x + 21.17,22. Num. 18.11,13; Rev. 3.11.\x*.
\v 8 Chakafa choga kana chakabvamburwa haangachidyi kuti azvisvibise nazvo; ndini Jehovha\x + 7.24.\x*.
\v 9 Naizvozvo vachachengeta murairo wangu kuti vasatakura chivi nekuda kwawo, vagofa nacho, kana vausvibisa; ndini Jehovha ndinovaita vatsvene\x + 19.17; Eki. 28.43.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Zvino kusava nemweni anodya chinhu chitsvene; agere nemupristi kana mushandi wakahaiwa* haangadyi chinhu chitsvene\x + 1 Sam. 21.6.\x*.
\v 11 Asi mupristi, kana akatenga munhu ari mutengo wemari yake, iye ungazvidya; uye anoberekerwa mumba make, ivo vachadya zvekudya zvake\x + Num. 18.11,13.\x*.
\v 12 Uye mwanasikana wemupristi, kana akava wemweni, iye haangadyi pachipo chezvinhu zvitsvene\x + Num. 18.11,13.\x*.
\v 13 Asi mwanasikana wemupristi, kana ari chirikadzi, kana warambiwa, uye asina mwana, akadzokera kumba kwababa vake\x + Gen. 38.11. Rut. 1.8.\x*, sepaudiki hwake, achadya zvekudya zvababa vake; asi hakungavi nemweni anodya pazviri\x + 10.14. Num. 18.11,19.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Zvino munhu, kana achidya chinhu chitsvene nekusaziva, achawedzera cheshanu chacho pachiri, agopa kumupristi chinhu chitsvene\x + 4.2; 5.15,16,18.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino havangasvibisi zvinhu zvitsvene zvevana vaIsraeri zvavanopa kuna Jehovha\x + Num. 18.32.\x*;
\v 16 vavaite vatakure kuipa kwemhosva, pavanodya zvinhu zvavo zvitsvene; nokuti ndini Jehovha ndinovaita vatsvene\x + 22.9.\x*.
\s Zvipo zvinofanira kuva zvakadini
\p
\v 17 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 18 Taura kuna Aroni nekuvanakomana vake nekuvana vaIsraeri vose ugoti kwavari: Ani nani weimba yaIsraeri kana wevatorwa pakati paIsraeri achapa chipo chake maererano nemhiko dzavo dzose nemaererano nezvose zvipo zvavo zvekuzvidira zvavanopa kuna Jehovha kuva chipo chinopiswa\x + 1.2,3,10. Num. 15.14.\x*;
\v 19 kuti mugamuchirike, mukono usina chaungapomerwa, wemombe, wemakwai, kana wembudzi\x + 1.3.\x*.
\v 20 Musapa chero chipi pachiri pane chipomerwa, nokuti hachingagamuchiriki kwamuri\x + Det. 15.21; 17.1. Mara. 1.8,14; VaHeb. 9.14. 1 Pet. 1.19.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino ani nani, kana anopa chibairo chezvipo zvekuyananisa kuna Jehovha\x + 3.1,6; 7.16.\x* kuzadzisa mhiko, kana chipo chekuzvidira, pamombe kana pamakwai, chinofanira kuva chakakwana kuti chigamuchirwe; hapangavi nechipomerwa chipi nechipi mazviri\x + Num. 15.3,8. Det. 23.21,23. Map. 61.8. 65.1. Mup. 5.4,5.\x*.
\v 22 Bofu kana chakavhunika kana chakaremara kana chine ronda rinoyerera \add ropa\x + 22.20. Mara. 1.8.\x*\add* kana chine chisasa kana chine mhizi\x + 21.20.\x*, hamungapi izvi kuna Jehovha, uye musapa pane izvi chipo chemoto kuna Jehovha paaritari\x + 1.9,13; 3.3,5.\x*.
\v 23 Asi nzombe diki kana gwayana zvine chakarebesa kana chakapfupika pamitezo mungapa kuva chipo chekuzvidira, asi pamhiko hazvingagamuchiriki\x + 21.18.\x*.
\v 24 Uye musapa kuna Jehovha chine \add manhu\add* akakuvara, kana akapwanyika, kana akaputswa, kana akachekwa; uye musa\add zvi\add*ita panyika yenyu.
\v 25 Nezvinobva muruoko rwemutorwa musapa zvekudya zvaMwari wenyu pane chimwe cheizvi\x + 3.11.\x*, nokuti kuipa kwazvo kuri mazviri, chipomerwa chiri mazviri, hazvingagamuchiriki kwamuri\x + Mara. 1.14.\x*.
\v 26 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 27 Kana nzombe diki kana gwai kana mbudzi zvichiberekwa, zvino zvichava pasi pamai vazvo mazuva manomwe. Uye kubva pazuva rerusere nekubva ipapo zvichagamuchirwa kuva chipo chechipo chemoto kuna Jehovha\x + Eki. 22.30.\x*.
\v 28 Uye nzombe kana gwai hamungariurayi pamwe nemwana waro pazuva rimwe\x + Det. 22.6.\x*.
\v 29 Uye kana muchibaira kuna Jehovha chibairo chekuvonga, muchabaira kuti mugamuchirike\x + 7.12. Map. 107.22. 116.17.\x*.
\v 30 Chichadyiwa nemusi iwoyo; hamungasii pachiri kusvika mangwana; ndini Jehovha\x + 7.15.\x*.
\v 31 Naizvozvo chengetai mirairo yangu, muiite; ndini Jehovha\x + 19.37. Num. 15.40. Det. 4.40.\x*.
\v 32 Uye musasvibisa zita rangu dzvene\x + 22.18,21.\x*; asi ndichaitwa mutsvene pakati pevana vaIsraeri; ndini Jehovha\x + 10.3.\x* anokuitai vatsvene\x + 20.8.\x*,
\v 33 akakubudisai panyika yeEgipita kuti ndive Mwari wenyu; ndini Jehovha\x + Eki. 6.7; Rev. 11.45; 19.36; 25.38,42,55; 26.45. Num. 15.41.\x*.